<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><workflow xmlns="http://www.cisco.com/cfr2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" fileFormatVersion="1" sdkVersion="3.0.30" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.cisco.com/cfr2 xdeProcedure.xsd">
    <import>TeTunnelFeature.vtl</import>
    <import>TeTunnel_fetch_mini.vtl</import>
    <import>XDE</import>
    <import>appendDocumentElements.xjs</import>
    <import>appendDocumentElementsAsString.xjs</import>
    <import>deviceSupportsForwarder.xpa</import>
    <import>fetchExplicitPathEntries.xde</import>
    <import>fetchProtocolEndPoint.vtl</import>
    <import>findNetworkElementIdFromDeviceId.xde</import>
    <import>getLatestCFSId.xde</import>
    <import>serviceFetchDefinitionTeTunnel.vtl</import>
    <import>system</import>
    <import>xmp-pp-helper-xde.xfn</import>
    <parameter>$serviceType</parameter>
    <parameter>$cfsId</parameter>
    <parameter>$operation</parameter>
    <parameter>$idAllocator</parameter>
    <parameter>$userData</parameter>
    <startStep id="Step1" next="sripuvva:150708123836453">
        <description/>
    </startStep>
    <javaScriptStep id="sripuvva:150708123836453" next="divyg:160725153218674">
        <description/>
        <script expressionType="js">var $subInterfaceMap = map.new();
if($operation == "CREATE" || $operation == "Ceased")  {
$cfsId = getLatestCFSId($cfsId); 
}

var $miniCfsFetch = TeTunnel_fetch_mini(map.new("tunnelCfsId", $cfsId));
system.log("CFS Mini Fetch ", $miniCfsFetch);
var $miniCfs = XMPPPFunctions.invokePersistenceMultiple($miniCfsFetch);

system.log("CFS Mini Fetch Output ", $miniCfs);

var $tunnelStatus = xml.xpathreference($miniCfs, "/beans/TeTunnelService/status/text()");

var $modelTemplate = xml.new(serviceFetchDefinitionTeTunnel(map.new("instanceId", $cfsId,"operation",$tunnelStatus)));

system.log("CFS Full Fetch Template", $modelTemplate);

var $model = XMPPPFunctions.invokePersistenceMultiple($modelTemplate);

system.log("CFS Full Fetch Output", $model);

var $src = "";
var $dest = "";
var $epSettings = xml.new();
var $srcEP = xml.new("<beans></beans>");
var $destEP = xml.new("<beans></beans>");



</script>
    </javaScriptStep>
    <javaScriptStep id="sripuvva:150714191111750" next="sripuvva:150714191146439">
        <description/>
        <script expressionType="js">var $featuresDocument = xml.new("<features/>");
var $teTunnelServiceName = xml.xpath($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/name/text()");
var $teTunnelServiceDescription = xml.xpath($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/description/text()");
var $protectionType = xml.xpath($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/protectionType/text()");
var $wrapenabled = xml.xpath($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/isWrapEnabled/text()");
var $serviceName = xml.xpath($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/name/text()");
system.log("isWrapEnabled value: ", $wrapenabled);</script>
    </javaScriptStep>
    <foreachStep id="sripuvva:150714191146439" next="Step2">
        <description/>
        <varname>$tetunnel</varname>
        <list expressionType="js">list.xpathreference($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/linkRFS0/aggregatedLinks/TeTunnel/linkTerminationPoints/TeTunnelFlowpoint", true)</list>
        <steps>
            <startStep id="sripuvva:150714191146439" next="sripuvva:150714191409144">
                <description/>
            </startStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="sripuvva:150714191409144" next="kvaidyan:151102185534882">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">$tetunnel = xml.new($tetunnel);
 
system.log("Te Tunnel Data ",$tetunnel);
 
var $teTunnelOwningEntityID = xml.xpath($tetunnel, "TeTunnelFlowpoint/owningEntityId/text()");
//var $epSettings = xml.new();
if(string.equalsIgnoreCase($teTunnelOwningEntityID, $src)) {
$epSettings = $srcEP;
} else if(string.equalsIgnoreCase($teTunnelOwningEntityID, $dest)) {
$epSettings = $destEP;
}
//var $deviceId = $teTunnelOwningEntityID.replace(/_.*/, "");
 
/*
var $teTunnelDestinationId = xml.xpath($tetunnel, "TeTunnelFlowpoint/teTunnelSettings/teTunnelDestination/TeTunnelDestination/@refInstanceId");
 
var $dpoModelTemplate = xml.new(serviceFetchDefinitionTeTunnelDPO(map.new("instanceId", $teTunnelDestinationId,"operation",$tunnelStatus,"preference",10)));
 
system.log("Active DPO Full Fetch Template", $dpoModelTemplate);
 
var $activeDpoModel = XMPPPFunctions.invokePersistenceMultiple($dpoModelTemplate);
 
system.log("Active DPO Full Fetch Output", $activeDpoModel);
 
 
var $protectedDpoModel = "";
var $restoreDpoModel = "";
 
if (string.eq($protectionType, "Working+Protected") || string.eq($protectionType, "Working+Protected+Restore")) {
    $dpoModelTemplate = xml.new(serviceFetchDefinitionTeTunnelDPO(map.new("instanceId", $teTunnelDestinationId,"operation",$tunnelStatus,"preference",20)));
 
   system.log("Protected DPO Full Fetch Template", $dpoModelTemplate);
 
   $protectedDpoModel = XMPPPFunctions.invokePersistenceMultiple($dpoModelTemplate);
 
   system.log("Protected DPO Full Fetch Output", $protectedDpoModel);
}
 
if (string.eq($protectionType, "Working+Restore") || string.eq($protectionType, "Working+Protected+Restore")) {
    $dpoModelTemplate = xml.new(serviceFetchDefinitionTeTunnelDPO(map.new("instanceId", $teTunnelDestinationId,"operation",$tunnelStatus,"preference",30)));
 
   system.log("Restore DPO Full Fetch Template", $dpoModelTemplate);
 
   $restoreDpoModel = XMPPPFunctions.invokePersistenceMultiple($dpoModelTemplate);
 
   system.log("Restore DPO Full Fetch Output", $restoreDpoModel);
}
*/
 
var $deviceId = $teTunnelOwningEntityID.split("_")[0];
 
//var $networkElementId = 223224;
 
//var $networkElementId = findNetworkElementIdFromDeviceId($deviceId);
 
system.log("Network Element Id is ", $deviceId);
 
 
var $isXR = deviceSupportsForwarder.supportsForwarder($deviceId);
 
system.log("Network Element isXR=", $isXR);
 
//$networkElementId = $networkElementId.split("_")[0];
 
var $teTunnelName = xml.xpath($tetunnel, "TeTunnelFlowpoint/name/text()");
var $isBFDEnable=TRUE;
var $minInterval = xml.xpath($tetunnel,"TeTunnelFlowpoint/teTunnelSettings/teTunnelBfdSettings/minInterval/text()");
if($minInterval==""){
   $isBFDEnable=FALSE;
}
 
if($operation=="DELETE") {
var deleteOD = xml.new();
if(map.exists($userData, "deleteOD"))
   deleteOD = xml.new(map.get($userData, "deleteOD"));
system.log("delete OD in deploy", deleteOD);
}
 
var $tunnelId=xml.xpath($tetunnel, "TeTunnelFlowpoint/teTunnelSettings/tunnelId/text()");
 
var $protocolEndPoint = fetchProtocolEndPoint(map.new("tunnelId", $tunnelId,"owningEntityId",$teTunnelOwningEntityID));
system.log("protocolEndPointData Fetch ", $protocolEndPoint);
var $protocolEndPointData = XMPPPFunctions.invokePersistenceMultiple($protocolEndPoint);
 
system.log("protocolEndPointData Fetch Output ", $protocolEndPointData);
var $activeLspId = xml.xpath($protocolEndPointData, "/beans/protocolEndpoint/activeLspId/text()");
var $standbyLspId = xml.xpath($protocolEndPointData, "/beans/protocolEndpoint/standbyLspId/text()");
var $adminStatus = xml.xpath($protocolEndPointData, "/beans/protocolEndpoint/adminStatus/text()");
if( $adminStatus==null || $adminStatus=="")
$adminStatus="UP";
var $operStatus = xml.xpath($protocolEndPointData, "/beans/protocolEndpoint/operStatus/text()");
var $ifIndex = xml.xpath($protocolEndPointData, "/beans/protocolEndpoint/ifIndex/text()");
if( $ifIndex==null ||  $ifIndex=="")
$ifIndex=0;
appendDocumentElementsAsString($featuresDocument, 
       TeTunnelFeature(map.new("tetunnel",$tetunnel,
                   "epSettings",$epSettings,
                   "tunnelCfsId", $cfsId,
                   "protectiontype", $protectionType,
                   "deviceId",$deviceId,
                   "teTunnelName",$teTunnelName,
                   "teTunnelOwningEntityID",$teTunnelOwningEntityID,
                   "idAllocator",$idAllocator,
                   "wrapenabled",$wrapenabled,
                   "serviceType",$serviceType,
                   "isBFDEnable",$isBFDEnable,
                   "operation",$operation,
                   "serviceName",$serviceName,
                   "deleteOD",deleteOD,
                   "isXR",$isXR,
                   "activeLspId",$activeLspId,
                   "standbyLspId",$standbyLspId,
                   "adminStatus",$adminStatus,
                   "operStatus",$operStatus,
                   "ifIndex",$ifIndex)));
 
system.log("Te Tunnel Feature Document ",$featuresDocument);</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="kvaidyan:151102185534882" next="sripuvva:150721060320823:1">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">$idAllocator = parseInt($idAllocator);
$idAllocator = $idAllocator + 1;</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
            <continueStep id="sripuvva:150721060320823:1">
                <description/>
            </continueStep>
        </steps>
    </foreachStep>
    <returnStep id="Step2">
        <description/>
        <result expressionType="js">$featuresDocument</result>
    </returnStep>
    <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725153218674" next="divyg:160818160952861">
        <description/>
        <script expressionType="js">var $explicitPaths = fetchExplicitPathEntries($cfsId,$model);
//system.log(xml.prettyPrint($explicitPaths));


$src = xml.xpath($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/linkRFS0/aggregatedLinks/TeTunnel[1]/linkTerminationPoints/TeTunnelFlowpoint/owningEntityId/text()");
if(string.eq($serviceType, "Bidirectional TE Tunnel")){
$dest = xml.xpath($model, "/beans/TeTunnelService/linkRFS0/aggregatedLinks/TeTunnel[2]/linkTerminationPoints/TeTunnelFlowpoint/owningEntityId/text()");
}
var exclusivePathsList = list.new();</script>
    </javaScriptStep>
    <foreachStep id="divyg:160725153845113" next="divyg:160725180643380">
        <description/>
        <varname>$EP</varname>
        <list expressionType="js">list.xpath(xml.new($explicitPaths), "/beans/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings")</list>
        <steps>
            <startStep id="divyg:160725153845113" next="divyg:160725153941637">
                <description/>
            </startStep>
            <continueStep id="divyg:160725153845113:1">
                <description/>
            </continueStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725153941637" next="divyg:160725155922958">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">//var $owningEntityId = xml.xpath($EP, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings/owningEntityId/text()")
var $name = xml.xpath($EP, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings/name/text()")




</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
            <foreachStep id="divyg:160725155906828" next="divyg:160725162001220">
                <description/>
                <varname>$items</varname>
                <list expressionType="js">list.xpath(xml.new($EP), "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings/entries/item")</list>
                <steps>
                    <startStep id="divyg:160725155906828" next="divyg:160725160131310">
                        <description/>
                    </startStep>
                    <continueStep id="divyg:160725155906828:1">
                        <description/>
                    </continueStep>
                    <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725160131310" next="divyg:160725155906828:1">
                        <description/>
                        <script expressionType="js">list.pushfront($listEP, $items);</script>
                    </javaScriptStep>
                </steps>
            </foreachStep>
            <ifStep else="divyg:160906182030704" id="divyg:160725155922958" then="divyg:160725160001603">
                <description/>
                <test expressionType="js">list.contains(exclusivePathsList, $name)</test>
            </ifStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725160001603" next="divyg:160725162646380">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">//$srcEP = xml.add($srcEP,"/beans",$EP);</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725162001220" next="divyg:160725162633763">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">for ( var i = 0 ; i < list.count($listEP); i = i + 1) { 

$epEntry = xml.add($epEntry, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings/entries", list.item($listEP, i))
} 
</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725162633763" next="divyg:160725153845113:1">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">$destEP = xml.add($destEP, "/beans", $epEntry)</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
            <continueStep id="divyg:160725162646380">
                <description/>
            </continueStep>
            <continueStep id="divyg:160725162701999">
                <description/>
            </continueStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725164350614" next="divyg:160725155906828">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">var $epEntry = xml.new("<TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings></TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings>");
$epEntry = xml.add($epEntry, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings", xml.xpath($EP, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings/name"))
$epEntry = xml.add($epEntry, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings", xml.xpath($EP, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings/owningEntityId"))
$epEntry = xml.add($epEntry, "/TeTunnelExplicitPathSettings", xml.new("<entries></entries>"))
var $listEP = list.new();</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
            <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160906182030704" next="divyg:160725164350614">
                <description/>
                <script expressionType="js">list.pushback(exclusivePathsList, $name)
$srcEP = xml.add($srcEP,"/beans",$EP);</script>
            </javaScriptStep>
        </steps>
    </foreachStep>
    <javaScriptStep id="divyg:160725180643380" next="sripuvva:150714191111750">
        <description/>
        <script expressionType="js">system.log("SRC EP xml", $srcEP);
system.log("DEST EP xml", $destEP);</script>
    </javaScriptStep>
    <ifStep else="divyg:160725180643380" id="divyg:160818160952861" then="divyg:160725153845113">
        <description/>
        <test expressionType="js">$explicitPaths != "__undefined__"</test>
    </ifStep>
</workflow>
